{"tid":1431733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"搭緊狗鐵，聽到班C9係到評論","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:01.000Z","uid":121048,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"664ffd07f7cd4d761f86a84cc29a727a1f1fa511","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"咁啱企咗係嗰三個C9隔離，聽到佢地係到討論呢幾日嘅行動。原本以為佢地三個係無腦藍絲，都準備好要還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知聽到有個C9講: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算唔支持班後生仔都好，都唔好去鬧佢地</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外兩個C9就點頭附和: 「咪係囉，最多咪唔出聲。」<br />\n<br />\n如果冇聽錯嘅話，當中仲有個C9有親手整過雞翼請班手足食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係隔離聽到真係唔知講咩好，嗰三個C9望落似係中產，估唔到我地玩完火、搞完不合作運動之後，佢地都冇同我地割𥱊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔好忽略C9嘅影響力，往往只要有一兩個C9出聲支持我地，就可以影響埋其他C9嘅思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以真係最好搞多啲地區放映會、派下傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5896f9f2a2c1f9b8e1d73cd0fd4215ed540af52","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"自己老母自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b550355c88b2080ae8ac499425aa62ee0d9299ea","tid":1431733,"uid":138144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"Be water be humble <br />\n不分化 不割席<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, the revolution of our time<br />\n<br />\n和你飛萬人接機 <br />\n8月9至11日 下午1時 <br />\n一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n<br />\n大埔遊行 <br />\n8月10日<br />\n大埔頭巴士總站 -&gt; 運頭角里投注站<br />\n<br />\n港島東遊行<br />\n8月11日 下午1時30分 <br />\n維多利亞公園 -&gt; 渣華道遊樂場<br />\n<br />\n深水埗遊行<br />\n8月11日 下午3時<br />\n楓樹街遊樂場 -&gt; 深水埗運動場<br />\n<br />\n8.16 學界-攬炒聯手萬人集會！國際本土戰線會師！第十攻！"},{"pid":"c264291885d270386069bbfde0383d502b77439a","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"和理非全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0d3407d919a5e2d2a94fb78184a0e9ed5ebfb4","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"仲有啊，人地班C9都冇話同我地割𥱊，我地更加唔應該自我分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n掉汽油彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bf3dba75ea52f5535d331292c7b5982db18312","tid":1431733,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"我已經成功令老母由中立變淺黃<br />\n依家日日個啊爸一講歪理就叫佢唔好嘈收聲 你落街講<br />\n仲叫我小心安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗚媽咪我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b828d9f877cdcafe6468b17485f625d35cd5a06","tid":1431733,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"勿做藍絲親中份子"},{"pid":"138a06ef2484cb76c07cc6960eb1f371e5d88e9f","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15bf3dba75ea52f5535d331292c7b5982db18312","tid":1431733,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"我已經成功令老母由中立變淺黃<br />\n依家日日個啊爸一講歪理就叫佢唔好嘈收聲 你落街講<br />\n仲叫我小心安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗚媽咪我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"我前幾日同老母嘈到反枱，但佢食完催淚彈之後又靜咗小小，我再同佢分析下，佢又正常翻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84510653d82d9a22ff23a56520e589bfec326b0","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b828d9f877cdcafe6468b17485f625d35cd5a06","tid":1431733,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"勿做藍絲親中份子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"要做多啲文宣，改變佢地嘅思想。<br />\n好多中年人其實係抗拒港獨，但如果同佢地解釋我地唔係爭取港獨，只係想要普選，佢地又會冇咁反對。<br />\n<br />\n我同我老母就係咁溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b2f3a661afd2be387f872dc0ceabc13491903d","tid":1431733,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"共產黨是有消滅後代的因子，是人類既毒瘤，要將所有人思想一式一樣，異己不能存在。"},{"pid":"d5d0291e9fc24d1806fb0e95392e072e8b4d04b7","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"其實班C9有仔有女，佢地見住班後生仔又流血又中彈，好自然會心軟。所以我地嘅文宣最好講多啲警方嘅濫權，點樣導致咁多人流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd95ea0689f07e5c380a1ef2d97f99a0d671634","tid":1431733,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f84510653d82d9a22ff23a56520e589bfec326b0","tid":1431733,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b828d9f877cdcafe6468b17485f625d35cd5a06","tid":1431733,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"勿做藍絲親中份子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"要做多啲文宣，改變佢地嘅思想。<br />\n好多中年人其實係抗拒港獨，但如果同佢地解釋我地唔係爭取港獨，只係想要普選，佢地又會冇咁反對。<br />\n<br />\n我同我老母就係咁溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"對, 宜家唔係要港獨, 順便宣傳叫人唔好親中, 順勢打擊建制<br />\nbtw, 建制都唔好叫建制喇, 叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">親中派</span></span></strong>啦"},{"pid":"17c3219ccb5bd558b223f88c7ddc560544a65fd2","tid":1431733,"uid":134178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"其實有d伯伯都好好 好可愛<br />\n<br />\n琴日有個伯伯係到摵連儂牆上面一張<br />\n「沒有暴徒只有暴政」既貼紙 <br />\n我同身旁既路人以為佢係想破壞 <br />\n於是就停低望住佢 <br />\n最後佢將個貼紙摵左出黎 <br />\n然後貼左係個電話背面 <br />\n我同路人望住伯伯呆一呆 <br />\n然後相視而笑"}]}